data.description: Enter this beautifully restored 1932 classic Norfolk Bungalow with wide front porch conveniently located to naval bases, interstates shopping coffeehouses, and restaurants. This home has many of the updates that you would expect including lovely oak floors, custom plantation shutters, updated kitchen, white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, walk-in laundry room. Updated baths. Two spacious downstairs bedrooms with a full bath in between. The second floor is your own private primary suite with bamboo flooring. Primary bath with double sinks, tub/shower.. New exterior vinyl siding and HVAC Gas Pack both in 2021. Hot water approx 6yrs old. 35yr roof approx 17yrs old. Temperature controlled attic vents 2008. Maintenance free backyard with paver patio & retractable awning. FP is decorative. Gar. in very good condition but as is. Annual flood ins.
